  h2(style='color: silver') Create-A-Car:
  div(style='color: silver')
    | Below you will find a series of options that will help us find the perfect car for you.
    br
    | If there is an option that you are unsure of, leave it blank! We will provide examples
    br
    | based on the other information that you have given us.
  br
  meta(name='viewport' content='width=100%, initial-scale=1')
  style.
    body {font-family: Arial;}
    /* Style the tab */
  #createACar.tabcontent
    form
      br
      |     Car brand:
      select(name='brand')
        option(value='1')  None
        option(value='2')  Ford
        option(value='3')  BMW
        option(value='4')  Toyoda
        option(value='5')  Lincoln
        option(value='6')  Subaru
      br
      br
      |     Type:
      select(name='type')
        option(value='1')  None
        option(value='2')  Sedan
        option(value='3')  Van
        option(value='4')  Truck
        option(value='5')  Convertable
        option(value='6')  Coupe
      br
      br
      fieldset
        legend  Package
        input#packageStandard(type='radio' name='package' value='standard')
        label(for='packageStandard')  Standard
        br
        input#packageSport(type='radio' name='package' value='sport')
        label(for='packageSport')  Sport
        br
        input#packageLimited(type='radio' name='package' value='limited')
        label(for='packageLimited')  Limited
        br
      br
      |     Interior color:
      select(name='intColor')
        option(value='1')  None
        option(value='2')  Red
        option(value='3')  Orange
        option(value='4')  Yellow
        option(value='5')  Green
        option(value='6')  Blue
        option(value='7')  Purple
        option(value='8')  Black
        option(value='9')  White
        option(value='10')  Pink
        option(value='11')  Silver
        option(value='12')  Brown
        option(value='13')  Gold
        option(value='14')  Tan
      br
      br
      |     Exterior color:
      select(name='extColor')
        option(value='1')  None
        option(value='2')  Red
        option(value='3')  Orange
        option(value='4')  Yellow
        option(value='5')  Green
        option(value='6')  Blue
        option(value='7')  Purple
        option(value='8')  Black
        option(value='9')  White
        option(value='10')  Pink
        option(value='11')  Silver
        option(value='12')  Brown
        option(value='13')  Gold
        option(value='14')  Tan
      br
      br
      |     Your starting price: 
      input(type='number' name='startPrice' min='5000' max='100000' step='1')
      br
      br
      button(onclick='car_create()')
        | Create
